				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/C%E1%BB%ADu-Ch%C3%A2n-s%C6%A1n-T%E1%BB%8Bnh-C%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B1-y%E1%BA%BFt-V%C3%B4-Ng%E1%BA%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%C3%A2n/poem-NvRRyFjTOVOf6TirXsToBA">Cửu Chân sơn, Tịnh Cư tự, yết Vô Ngại thượng nhân - 九真山淨居寺謁無礙上 人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/H%C3%A1-H%E1%BA%A1-Ch%C3%A2u-t%E1%BA%A1p-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-08/poem-8DKvfPE4ThDG2ZFI0H5BJw">Há Hạ Châu tạp ký kỳ 08 - 下賀洲雜記其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Duy-Thi%E1%BB%87n/Luy%E1%BB%87n-v%C5%A9-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-3RI8Z0yFFhwIcCra6GId9A">Luyện vũ trường - 鍊武塲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Duy-Thi%E1%BB%87n/author-20zOUYXmZ1vM3bPi5n3bGw">Vũ Duy Thiện</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-02/poem-1eHT9uUwMooz1A2PSi3vCw">Nhàn vịnh kỳ 02 - 間詠其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/%C3%94-%C3%B4-ca/poem--nkwKog4rhovNtymFbWpRg">Ô ô ca - 烏烏歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nh%E1%BA%A1c-L%C3%B4i-Ph%C3%A1t/author-5J0P_EDGEC1h1gar2eA3WQ">Nhạc Lôi Phát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BA%B7ng-b%E1%BA%A3n-huy%E1%BB%87n-hu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-Trang-Li%E1%BB%87t-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-th%C4%83ng-bi%C3%AAn-tu-sung-gi%E1%BA%A3ng-t%E1%BA%ADp/poem-m-Dj2kroUbeo4b45J0W2iQ">Tặng bản huyện huấn đạo Trang Liệt Nguyễn thăng biên tu sung giảng tập - 贈本縣訓導莊烈阮升編修充講習</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Minh-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-D%C6%B0-Qu%C3%BD/poem-1hyRItLEA1i4A9mVsfb2iQ">Tống Đại Minh quốc sứ Dư Quý - 送大明國使余貴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%E1%BB%91ng-t%C4%83ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Khi%C3%AAm-quy-s%C6%A1n/poem-yg1VDNAzKt7flR4lVTS7qw">Tống tăng Đạo Khiêm quy sơn - 送僧道謙歸山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/V%C3%A3n-Ph%C3%A1p-Loa-t%C3%B4n-gi%E1%BA%A3-Thanh-Mai-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-4hxwNBM2h4AsuA1hvhLkJA">Vãn Pháp Loa tôn giả Thanh Mai tự - 挽法螺尊者題青梅寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Minh-T%C3%B4ng/author-4trx3YJ-cefKhX0g_XM7Sw">Trần Minh Tông</a>)<br></div>	</div>
